<style src="./TSView.css"></style>
<template src="./TSView.html"></template>
<script>
    import ViewtitleComponent from '@/components/ViewtitleComponent/ViewtitleComponent.vue'

    export default {
        name: "TSView",
        data() {
            return {
                areaName: "TypeScript",
                logo_link: "https://logodix.com/logo/1193669.png",
                links_list: [
                    {link: "https://www.typescriptlang.org/", title: "Оффициальный сайт"},
                ]
            }
        },
        components: {
            ViewtitleComponent,
        },
        provide() {
            return {
                areaName: this.areaName,
                logoLink: this.logo_link,
            }
        }
    }
</script>
